"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-uk-1932336-olympics-viewers-only-just-realising-team-gb-uk\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The Paris Olympics may have got off to a rocky opening ceremony start but Team GB has had a great Games in 2024 so far, with a haul of 38 medals including 10 golds so far, putting us sixth in the overall table well ahead of the likes of Germany, Japan and Ireland.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.6873403295945837, \"rank\": 0.4070373203854498, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9712635296733596, \"rank\": 0.01609394293280104, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9970822742785624, \"rank\": 0.002898985426597981, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one thing manyOlympicsviewers have noticed on theBBCis that the competitors - whether it's Max Whitlock, Alex Yee or Beth Potter, have all been competing for 'Team Great Britain and Northern Ireland', according to commentators on the live BBC coverage.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9828473642916633, \"rank\": 0.01436979045087104, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But how can it be Team GB if it includes Northern Ireland - and why is not it Team UK, then?\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\