ball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.8936276157804429, \"rank\": 0.11800749016162769, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9865444347794791, \"rank\": 0.013440361027215192, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.999999258323944, \"rank\": 6.281254730512898e-07, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999959504748, \"rank\": 2.7551254246372225e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the UK puts forward one combined team for the country - and then called it Team GB, which viewers have noticed.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999959504748, \"rank\": 2.7551254246372225e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Geographically, Great Britain only refers to the mainland landmass of England, Scotland and Wales and does not include Northern Ireland.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991350038375, \"rank\": 4.449264322890512e-07, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.994373235993125, \"rank\": 0.004697863205683378, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9865444347794791, \"rank\": 0.013440361027215192, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.8936276157804429, \"rank\": 0.11800749016162769, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Northern Irish athletes are part of Team GB unless they choose to compete for the Republic of Ireland.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"u/Brainfreeze asked onReddit: \\\"Team GB.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not Team UK?\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999959504748, \"rank\": 2.7551254246372225e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It seems as though NI gets left out.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2417489984370956e-19, \"text\": \"NI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of geography Great Britain is the name of an island.\\\"\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991350038375, \"rank\": 4.449264322890512e-07, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One poster replied: \\\"Officially it's the Great Britain and Northern Ireland Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB was picked in 1999 as a snappy marketing tool.\\\"\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@saltire_blue said: \\\"Similar to why the England and Wales cricket team is called simply \\\"England.\\\"\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.994373235993125, \"rank\": 0.004697863205683378, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.8936276157804429, \"rank\": 0.11800749016162769, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They claimed it was marketing reasons to whitewash Wales out the team name and the governing body.\\\"\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.8936276157804429, \"rank\": 0.11800749016162769, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@ducra replied: \\\"But it is no more snappy than Team UK, is it?\\\"\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999959504748, \"rank\": 2.7551254246372225e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, @orgpenguin explained: \\\"It goes back to when the British Olympic Committee was set up yonks ago to cover all British Isles and a number of other territories, including what is now the Irish Republic.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Isles\", \"score\": 0.5529084905585856, \"rank\": 0.7923171106493148, \"text\": \"British Isles\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Isles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Isles\"}, {\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999740631227169, \"rank\": 2.593755012127437e-05, \"text\": \"Irish Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic identity since then has been \\\"GBR\\\", which evolved into Team GB.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand the BOC argue that because the team still covers the likes of Jersey, Channel Islands and such that Team UK would be even more inaccurate.\\\"\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bell_System\", \"score\": 0.7393284508053112, \"rank\": 0.33193994755477835, \"text\": \"BOC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bell_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bell_System\"}, {\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999959504748, \"rank\": 2.7551254246372225e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was taken in 1999, after the British Olympic Association director of marketing decided that the official Great Britain and Northern Ireland Olympic team name was too much of a mouthful, and she masterminded the Team GB concept.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991350038375, \"rank\": 4.449264322890512e-07, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2659, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.824252787885672, \"rank\": 0.19349485493547913, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The name has since attracted criticism, with one Northern Irish minister claiming the name \\\"excludes and alienates\\\" people from Northern Ireland.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999698382726, \"rank\": 2.1053307735429248e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Irish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2805, \"end\": 2821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998849134566, \"rank\": 1.1499193868526016e-07, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi